data.description: Darling home situated on a large lot located on a cul-de-sac street.  Fabulous location that is close to downtown, shopping, restaurants, and easy freeway access.  4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with 1,300 sq. ft. of living space and 2 car attached garage. Large screened in front porch that adds extra living/ entertaining space. The kitchen has been updated and upgraded with white cabinetry, new brushed nickel hardware, solid countertops, stainless steel stink, new faucet, light fixtures, and newer appliances.  Kitchen opens to the dining room and spacious family room.   Down the hall you will find the master bedroom suite with full bathroom and 3 secondary bedrooms with walk in closets and a guest bathroom. New laminate wood flooring throughout common areas with new plush carpet in the bedrooms. New window blinds throughout the home and new AC to keep you cool throughout the warm summer months. French doors off the dining room lead you out to a large backyard. Large storage shed in the backyard for everything you may need to keep out of the sun/ weather. Front yard has artificial turf so there is low/ no maintenance. Long driveway for extra parking and potential RV parking on the side of the home. Super low taxes and No HOA. Enjoy all that this home and neighborhood have to offer. Come check it out today-- it will be gone quick!
